  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The second three Uriel Ventris novels under Black Library's 'Chronicles' reissue branding — The Killing Ground, Courage and Honour, and The Chapter's Due — content unchanged from the older Second Omnibus. The arc that follows Uriel and Pasanius back out of the Eye of Terror: first to Salinas, where a Governor's old massacre still poisons the ground and the Unfleshed who followed Uriel out of Medrengard come for their own kin; then to Pavonis again, this time against a Tau Empire invasion split between a Hunter Cadre's lines and a Water-Caste envoy's quieter politics; finally to Ultramar itself, as Honsou's Skull Harvest pulls the Iron Warriors' grudge to sector scale. Not an entry-point — start with Vol. 1.",
